.000Z","msg":"咁你做乜叫我入嚟啫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:10:03.000Z","msg":"叫你入黎問你成家短命種幾時死撚晒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:10:51.000Z","msg":"咁我唔入嚟囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:14:15.000Z","msg":"死遠啲啦"},{"pid":"3be47f039d3ec07769618e67687bd31e81daeb7d","tid":1527561,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T19:35:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">左膠永遠都唔係同路人<br />\n<br />\n荃灣黑夜 要前線放藍衫走<br />\n結果同一班藍衫轉頭斬斷其他手足手筋腳筋攪到個手足殘廢 同有手足比人爆頭<br />\n到今日岩岩機場 逼手足放個用磚頭爆手足頭既藍絲走<br />\n<br />\n重有依2個月好多單左膠死攬傷人者<br />\n根本班撚樣只係為光環 欺善怕惡<br />\n對住黑社會就淆底唔敢阻黑社會斬人<br />\n對住自己手足 知手足唔會打佢地<br />\n就大大力阻手足還拖 同講廢話訓前線話<br />\n話會扣幾多分 會失民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"cfb9c6c09a657a11837ca1e9ac3e9f2726f7caa5","tid":1527561,"uid":61417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T19:36:11.000Z","msg":"屌，幫手推下有用post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我要報平安，我要搵律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［人手置頂］被捕需知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529663\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529663</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}